<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<tal:block tal:content="structure python:here.zmi_html_head(here,request)">zmi_html_head</tal:block>
<body tal:attributes="class python:' '.join(['zmi',request['lang'],'main',here.meta_id])">
<form class="form-horizontal" action="manage_changeProperties" method="post">

<legend>
	<a href="manage_main">
		<i tal:attributes="class python:here.icon_clazz"></i>
		<tal:block tal:content="python:here.meta_type">the meta_type</tal:block>
	</a>
</legend>

<p class="well">
A Sequence is used to provide unique ids. You can update the current value using the form below.
</p>

<div class="control-group">
	<label class="control-label" for="currentvalue:int"><span>Current-Value</span></label>
	<div class="controls"><input type="text" name="currentvalue:int" size="8" tal:attributes="value python:here.currVal()"/></div><!-- .controls -->
</div><!-- .control-group -->

<div class="control-group">
	<div class="controls">
		<button name="submit" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="Change">Change</button>
		<button name="submit" type="submit" class="btn" value="Next">Next</button>
	</div><!-- .controls -->
</div><!-- .control-group -->

</form>
</body>
</html>